OL,3,CScottish man jailed after smuggling
OL,4,Ccocaine into Jersey to clear debt
OL,6,FA 37-year-old man from Dumfries has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed after smuggling just under
OL,8,F100 grams of cocaine into Jersey.
OL,10,FRobert Martin Allan, 37, was stopped
OL,11,Fby customs officers at Jersey Airport
OL,12,Fon Thursday 18 September, after
OL,13,Farriving on a flight from Glasgow.
OL,15,FHe was supposedly visiting the island
OL,16,Ffor two days, but said he knew no one
OL,17,Fand had not been there before.
OL,19,FOfficials found Allan only had #35 on
OL,20,Fhim and was unemployed.
