OL,3,CScottish man jailed after smuggling
OL,4,Ccocaine into Jersey to clear debt
OL,6,FHe admitted to using cannabis and
OL,7,Fcocaine, with swab tests from his bag
OL,8,Fflagging positive for the latter Class
OL,9,FA substance.
OL,11,FCustoms officers became suspicious
OL,12,Fthat the traveller was carrying drugs
OL,13,Finternally and arrested him, with a CT
OL,14,Fscan later showing seven packages
OL,15,Finside him.
OL,17,FThey turned out to be cocaine with a
OL,18,Fcombined weight of 98.56 grams and a
OL,19,Fstreet value of #25,000.
