OL,3,CScottish man jailed after smuggling
OL,4,Ccocaine into Jersey to clear debt
OL,6,FWhen he was interviewed, Allan claimed
OL,7,Fhe had built up a drug debt of around
OL,8,F#1,000 and had been threatened in
OL,9,FDumfries to import the drugs to Jersey
OL,10,Fto clear his name.
OL,12,FAllan was sentenced to six years and
OL,13,Fnine months in prison by Jersey's
OL,14,FRoyal Court.
OL,16,FPaul Le Monnier, Senior Manager at
OL,17,FJersey Customs and Immigration
OL,18,FService, explains: "Drug importations
OL,19,Fcause serious harm to our community
OL,20,Fand fuel organised crime.
